    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80f4-ba42-e93cf95c211f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Selecting an approppriate undergraduate degree is of the utmost importance to high school students. The authors use multiple interpretable classifiers to predict the most approppriate undergraduate degre for a given student. ",
