    {
      "id": "1924750c-f3ba-80bd-85b7-d8ef94c35912",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The statistical results show that higher student marks in higher secondary (hsc_p), university degree (Degree_p), and entry test (etest_p) play an important role in the student’s area of specialization, and we can recommend study fields according to these features.",
